# xrootd

On sci-xrootd.jlab.org : /osgpool/hallb/

On CUE machines:
/work/osgpool/hallb/ is rsync'ed (with delete) to the server every 4hrs.

On-site:
setenv LD_PRELOAD /usr/lib64/libXrdPosixPreload.so
ls xroot://sci-xrootd-ib//osgpool/hallb/

Off-site:
setenv LD_PRELOAD <path-to-lib>/libXrdPosixPreload.so
ls xroot://sci-xrootd.jlab.org//osgpool/hallb/


# Background merging files

They are on  /work/osgpool/hallb/clas12/backgroundfiles/

The structure:

- Each top dir is an experiment configuration
- Each configuration contains a list of possible fields combinations
- Each field configurations contains a list of possible beam current / energy configurations


